items.title: Stock Radar: NTPC Green Energy, Siemens, Zee Entertainment, Kotak Bank, Zaggle, Wipro, Dabur in focus on Wednesday
items.description: Stocks like Devyani International, Exide Industries, UltraTech Cement, Adani Enterprises, GE Vernova T&D India, NTPC, Patanjali Foods, Agarwal Industrial Corporation, A B Infrabuild, and Ola Electric Mobility will also be in focus on November 27.
